data.description: Welcome to this stunning 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home situated on a large corner lot located in Aspen Grove community in Western Henrico. This home opens to spacious family room with a fireplace to enjoy during cooler months. The family room extends to a beautiful sun filled Florida Room.  The kitchen is nicely sized with a dining area and a large window that lets in sunlight that brightens the room. Upstairs you will enjoy 3 spacious bedrooms.  The primary suite has its own private bath and a second full hallway bathroom.  All carpets have been updated to beautiful LVP flooring. The Florida room leads out to a semi-private rear deck perfect for family cookouts and entertaining friends. A detached shed at the rear of the yard to store personal belongings.  This home location is close to restaurants, stores and easy access to the interstate.  Don't miss this opportunity to live in a lovely home in a great community.
